For engraved portraits of Owen see first edition of Palmer’s Nonconformists' Memorial and Vertue’s Sermons and
                    Tracts, 1721. The chief authorities for the life are Owen’s Works; Orme’s Memoirs of Owen; Wood’s
                    Athena Oxonienses; Baxter’s Life;
                    Neal’s History of theParitans;
                    Edwards’s Gangraena; and the various histories of the
                    Independents. (O. A.)
